item.title: Why Cant i spawn

item.description:

Ya its simple, just open Client.java… hold down ctrl and f . inside the box type admin list

a list should come up and it should look like this

//start of moderator/admin list, 1 = mod, 2 = staff, 3 = admin
if (playerName.equalsIgnoreCase(" ")

inside the " take out the name and put ur ingame name

then right below that u shoudl c playerRights put this playerRights = 2; and ur set save & compile
